<img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1180" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/sanchez-168x300.jpg" alt="" width="168" height="300" />
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Leaked image of Alexis Sanchez in Manchester United Kit</strong></p>
